content: The autograder for PSET 2 gave me a zero even though my code passed all the test cases provided. On the results page, it says "Your code passed 0 public tests for 0.0000 points out of 0.0000." Will my code be regraded manually?
subject: 0% With PSET 2 autograder

content: <md>If you received a zero on the pset, we take a look at it via manual grading to see if a simple mistake somewhere messed up the test cases.</md>
